CREATE TABLE keychain ( userID INT NOT NULL , applicationID INT NOT NULL , username VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL , password VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL , PRIMARY KEY (userID, applicationID) );
DELETE keychain.* FROM keychain, application, user WHERE keychain.applicationID=application.id AND application.name="{application}" AND keychain.userID=user.id AND user.name="{user}"
SELECT id FROM application WHERE name="{application}"
SELECT * FROM application ORDER BY name

SELECT keychain.username, keychain.password FROM keychain, user, application WHERE keychain.applicationID=application.id AND application.name="{application}" AND keychain.userID=user.id AND user.name="{user}"
SELECT id FROM user WHERE name="{user}"

SELECT keychain.userID, keychain.username, keychain.applicationID, application.name AS application FROM application, keychain, user WHERE keychain.userID = user.id AND keychain.applicationID = application.id AND user.name = "{user}" ORDER BY application;

SELECT * FROM application WHERE application.id NOT IN ( SELECT keychain.applicationID FROM application, keychain, user WHERE keychain.userID = user.id AND application.ID = keychain.applicationID AND user.name = "{user}" ) ORDER BY application.name;
